'''Leo Lefford''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. He is played by guest star [[Vinnie McCabe]] and debuts in &quot;[[Baelor]].&quot; Leo Lefford is the head of [[House Lefford]] and Lord of the [[Golden Tooth]]. He is fighting for his liege lord [[Tywin Lannister]] in the [[War of the Five Kings]].

